    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owner. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as expected, making it a reliable choice for daily use. While the exterior shows some minor signs of age like small paint chips, the body is straight and free of major damage. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all electronic features and climate control working perfectly. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car that offers great value for its next owner.",
