    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior paint retains a deep luster, though a close inspection reveals some minor rock chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches near the trunk area. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a documented service history, making it a dependable choice for its next owner.",
      "price": 35000.0,
